snippet.title: AQUAMAN 2 (2022) Teaser Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard (Fan Made)
snippet.description: Aquaman has been blinded in a mysterious event. Years have passed and soon he regains his sight. However, damage to his land has been done. Its up to him and Mera to find out what happened. Hey guys I would like to make it clear that this trailer is fan made. That means it contains clips from other movies, put together with special effects using Wondershare Filmora video editor and Photopea (Photopea.com) photo editor.
